text: Hemicladus buqueti is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tavakilian, Touroult and Dalens in 2010. It is known from Guyana.BioLib.cz - Hemicladus buqueti. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 2010
